title: An Evening of Geet & Ghazal with Taranam Naz & Naeem Abbas Rufi
desc: A mesmerizing evening with Pakistan's two sensational voice, Taranam Naz with melodious voice along with Naeem Abbas Rufi, to tribute Pakistani legendary singers like Madam Noor Jahan , Farida Khanam, Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan, Ustad Amanat Ali Khan and many more... .
